text: Annie Khalid or just Annie (or real name Noor al Ain Khalid) (born 1987) is a British-Pakistani music star and diva.Pakistan Music Mag Fri, 10 May 2013, p 3 She started her career in 2006. She sings in Urdu, Punjabi and English languages. Her major hit singles so far include Mahiya (2007), Awarapan (2007), By my Baby (2010), Vari vari jawan (2011) and Tharki sala (2014). Her best-selling album so far is Princess. Annie was for a short time married to a criminal multi-millionaire Pakistani, settled in Dubai, called Malik Noureed Awan.http://gulfnews.com/about-gulf-news/al-nisr- portfolio/xpress/news/dramatic-rise-and-fall-of-jailed-mma-group-businessman Retrieved 12 Sept 2014 But this man was very violenthttp://www.thenews.com.pk/article-65894-Pop-star-Annies-nuptials- spoiled Retrieved 12 Sept 2014 and he used to beat and abuse her, so she left him. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:British Pakistanis Category:English pop singers
